  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="question-text">
      What are two ICMPv6 messages that are not present in ICMP for IPv4? (Choose two.)
    </p>
    <div class="options" id="opts-87">
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="0">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
